## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-161">以前に作成した <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>に <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> プロパティが割り当てられている場合、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> は複製されません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-161">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> property is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-162">代わりに、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> は、以前に作成した <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>への参照を保持します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-162">Instead, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-163">更新操作中に <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> が設定されておらず、<xref:System.Data.DataSet>に主キー情報が存在する場合は、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> クラスを使用して、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>を自動的に生成したり、<xref:System.Data.DataSet> をデータベースに調整するために必要な追加のコマンドを実行したりできます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-163">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-164">これを行うには、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>の <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> プロパティを設定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-164">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-165">また、生成ロジックでは、キー列情報が <xref:System.Data.DataSet>に存在する必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-165">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-166">詳細については、「 [CommandBuilders を使用したコマンドの生成](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md)」を参照してください。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-166">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-167">次の例では、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> を作成し、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> プロパティと <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> プロパティを設定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-167">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.DeleteCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-168"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> オブジェクトが既に作成されていることを前提としています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-168">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   
  
  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  Dim parm As OracleParameter  
  
  ' Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd  
  
  ' Create the DeleteCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", conn)  
  
  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original  
  
  da.DeleteCommand = cmd  
  
  Return da  
End Function  
```  
  
```csharp  
public static OracleDataAdapter CreateCustomerAdapter(OracleConnection conn)  
{  
  OracleDataAdapter da = new OracleDataAdapter();  
  OracleCommand cmd;  
  OracleParameter parm;  
  
  // Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " +  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn);  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14);  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13);  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd;  
  
  // Create the DeleteCommand.  
  
  cmd = new OracleCommand("DELETE FROM Dept WHERE DeptNo = :pDeptNo", conn);  
  
  parm = cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo");  
  parm.SourceVersion = DataRowVersion.Original;  
  
  da.DeleteCommand = cmd;  
  
  return da;  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-172">以前に作成された <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> オブジェクトに <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> プロパティが割り当てられている場合、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> は複製されません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-172">When the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> property is assigned to a previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object, the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> is not cloned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-173">代わりに、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> は、以前に作成した <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>への参照を保持します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-173">Instead, <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> maintains a reference to the previously created <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-174">更新操作中に <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> が設定されておらず、<xref:System.Data.DataSet>に主キー情報が存在する場合は、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> クラスを使用して、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>、およびデータベースに対する <xref:System.Data.DataSet> の調整に必要な追加のコマンドを自動的に生成できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-174">During an update operation, if <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> is not set and primary key information is present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>, you can use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommandBuilder> class to automatically generate <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A>, and additional commands needed to reconcile the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> to the database.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-175">これを行うには、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>の <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> プロパティを設定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-175">To do this, set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-176">また、生成ロジックでは、キー列情報が <xref:System.Data.DataSet>に存在する必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-176">The generation logic also requires key column information to be present in the <xref:System.Data.DataSet>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-177">詳細については、「 [CommandBuilders を使用したコマンドの生成](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md)」を参照してください。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-177">For more information see [Generating Commands with CommandBuilders](~/docs/framework/data/adonet/generating-commands-with-commandbuilders.md).</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-178">このコマンドの実行によって行が返される場合、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> オブジェクトの <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A> プロパティの設定方法によっては、これらの行が <xref:System.Data.DataSet> に追加されることがあります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-178">If execution of this command returns rows, these rows may be added to the <xref:System.Data.DataSet> depending upon how you set the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand.UpdatedRowSource%2A> property of the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleCommand> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-179">`LONG RAW` データ型の列を更新すると、列に `NULL` の値を入力したときに例外がスローされます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-179">When you update a column with the `LONG RAW` data type, an exception is thrown when you enter a value of `NULL` in the column.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-180">Oracle の `LONG RAW` データ型は、Oracle バージョン8.0 で非推奨とされた型です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-180">The Oracle `LONG RAW` data type is a deprecated type in Oracle version 8.0.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-181">このエラーを回避するには、`LONG RAW`ではなく `BLOB` データ型を使用します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-181">To avoid this error, use the `BLOB` data type instead of `LONG RAW`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-182">次の例では、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> を作成し、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> プロパティと <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> プロパティを設定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-182">The following example creates an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter> and sets the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.SelectCommand%2A> and <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataAdapter.InsertCommand%2A> properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6a07f-183"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> オブジェクトが既に作成されていることを前提としています。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6a07f-183">It assumes you have already created an <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleConnection> object.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Shared Function CreateCustomerAdapter(conn As OracleConnection) As OracleDataAdapter   
  
  Dim da As OracleDataAdapter = New OracleDataAdapter()  
  Dim cmd As OracleCommand  
  
  ' Create the SelectCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("SELECT * FROM Dept " & _  
                       "WHERE DName = :pDName AND Loc = :pLoc", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14)  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pLoc", OracleType.NVarChar, 13)  
  
  da.SelectCommand = cmd  
  
  ' Create the InsertCommand.  
  
  cmd = New OracleCommand("INSERT INTO Dept (DeptNo, DName) " & _  
                       "VALUES (:pDeptNo, :pDName)", conn)  
  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDeptNo", OracleType.Number, 2, "DeptNo")  
  cmd.Parameters.Add("pDName", OracleType.NVarChar, 14, "DName")  
  
  da.InsertCommand = cmd  
  
  Return da  
End Function  
